### Powering Your Off-Grid Vertical Garden


For sustained, self-sufficient operation, we recommend pairing it with **HotCarrier™** Solar Panels. A complimentary drone survey of your location will assess sunlight exposure to determine the optimal panel size and placement for maximum energy generation, even in low-light conditions.

